<div class="listings">
<h2>Operation Menu</h2>

<ul>
  <li>[inbox] ... show inbox; inbox shows unread entries in 'Home' feed</li>
  <li>[pin] ... show pinned entries</li>
  <li>[post] ... add new entry</li>
  <li>[search] ... search entries</li>
  <li>[settings] ... change session settings</li>
  <li>[help] ... show this help</li>
  <li>[logout] ... logout and discard settings</li>
</ul>

<h2>Page Cursor</h2>
<ul>
  <li>[&lt;] ... go previous page</li>
  <li>[from the top] ... show first entry of the list</li>
  <li>[&gt;] ... go next page</li>
</ul>

<h2>Entry Edit Operation</h2>

<ul>
  <li>[like] ... add 'like'</li>
  <li>&gt;&gt;&gt; ... add comment</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:star) %> ... show who 'like'd it; delete your 'like' once you 'like'd it</li>
</ul>

<h2>Pin Operation</h2>

<ul>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:pin) %> ... add pin to the entry; pinned entries keep on showing in [inbox] and [pin]</li>
  <li><%= icon_tag(:pinned) %> ... unpin the entry and archive it</li>
  <li><%= submit_tag('mark as read') %> ... archive entries except pinned entries</li>
</ul>

</div>

